      "translations": {
        "en": "――Magazine shoot day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2.6333332698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "ふおぉぉ……懐かしの我が家……たぎる……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoaaa… my nostalgic home… I'm fired up…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.6333332698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.3666666031
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "まずは水と寝床の確保……\nそれから火起こしの道具を一式揃えて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First‚ secure water and sleeping arrangements…\nThen gather a complete set of fire-making tools…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日の撮影は数時間で終わるから\nそこまでしなくていいんだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today's shoot will be over in a few hours‚\nso you don't need to go that far.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.5333332698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "……ハッ！　あれは……\nロケで遙子さんが大鉈を振るって作ったブランコ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah! That is…\nThe swing that Haruko-san made by wielding a big hatchet during the shoot…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.3333332698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "本来の意味じゃなくて\n文字通りの意味なんだな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not in the original sense‚\nbut in the literal sense…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.5999999364
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "「そんな技術があるなら\nまずはいかだを作った方が良くないですか？」って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"If you have that kind of skill‚\nwouldn't it be better to make a raft first?\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんが怜ちゃんに冷静にツッコまれて\nショックを受けてたのもいい思い出……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san was calmly called out by Rei-chan\nand was shocked - that's also a good memory…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今日はインタビューも兼ねているから\nそういう思い出もどんどん話してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since today also includes an interview‚\nplease share those kinds of memories freely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.9174391588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.4333347957
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "任せて……私がプライベートでバッチリ収めた\n秘蔵映像も一部公開するから……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Leave it to me… I'll also partially release some of\nthe secret footage I privately captured…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.4000001908
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "えっ。いや、さすがにそれはやめておいた方が\nいいんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh. No‚ I think you should probably\navoid doing that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫……ちゃんとみんなの了承はもらってるから\n……怜ちゃんはもの凄く迷ってたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay… I got everyone's permission properly‚\n…Rei-chan was really hesitant‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（インタビューが始まったな……）\n（ちゃんと答えられるといいんだが）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The interview has started…）\n（I hope she can answer properly）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "自分がロケで頑張ったことは……えっと\nみんなの頑張りをちゃんとカメラに収める……こと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What I worked hard on during the shoot is… um\nproperly capturing everyone's efforts on camera…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.8000006994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、私が撮った映像を観ながら話していい……ですか？\nそ、それなら……お任せあれ、です……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ can I talk while watching the footage I shot…?\nTh-then… leave it to me…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.8666653316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "これは……朝が弱い怜ちゃんが\n日光を避けようところころ転がってるところで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is… Rei-chan‚ who's not good with mornings‚\nrolling around trying to avoid sunlight…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "こっちは、さくらちゃんが海を見ながら\n「とんかつが恋しい……」って呟いてるところ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This one is Sakura-chan looking at the sea\nand murmuring \"I miss tonkatsu…\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.7666653316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "あとは、遙子さんがナタを持ってキレッキレの動きで\n寝床を作ってるところ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And here's Haruko-san with sharp movements holding a hatchet‚\nmaking sleeping arrangements…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.6427954357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（だんだん雫のスイッチが入ってきたな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Shizuku is gradually getting into her groove）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.0666653316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.5666653316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "後は……千紗ちゃんが「こういう茂みから怖いピエロが\n出て来る映画があったなぁ」って話した瞬間……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then… the moment Chisa-chan said \"There was a movie\nwhere a scary clown came out of bushes like this\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.6666678747
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "その茂みからがさがさって音がして、みんなパニックに\nなってダッシュで逃げたところ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There was a rustling sound from that bush‚ everyone panicked\nand ran away at full speed…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.5000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "結局、蛇か何かみたいだったんだけど……\nタイミングが悪過ぎて心臓がキュッてなった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It turned out to be a snake or something‚ but…\nthe timing was so bad it made my heart skip…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.8333345414
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "……ハッ！　す、すみません\n一杯喋り過ぎちゃいました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah! S-sorry‚\nI talked way too much…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.4999951046
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_08_03-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "……これくらい話してくれた方がありがたい、ですか？\nほっ……それなら、良かったです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're grateful when I talk this much?\nPhew… then that's good…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
